snippet.title: SPLITSCREEN Multiplayer Is Here! (Zelda BotW)
snippet.description:
In today's video we will be taking a look at the brand-new Multiplayer Splitscreen mod for Zelda Breath of the Wild from Kirbimini. Splitscreen version will be released on 29th July 2022. It's currently in Beta so expect issues to be fixed in the future. 

Check out Kirbymimi and my second player Orcacle:

Kirbymimi's Discord server (Download): https://discord.com/invite/ZPvZm3NFak
Multiplayer Mod site: https://gamebanana.com/mods/388450
Orcacle's channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_ZAh1BMU2Bd8J556t0cbgQ

✨ Join my Discord: https://discord.gg/ZU5cPYbYWZ
❤️ Support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/waikuteru
🍌 GameBanana account: https://gamebanana.com/members/1676542

#Zelda #BreathOfTheWild #DLC
